{"tid":2182220,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"九月復課就冇問題，投票就極高風險","createTime":"2020-08-31T07:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T08:01:30.000Z","uid":154406,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b30edada773f2ed4ad1694bfb555a96baeec730","tid":2182220,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"政府宣布9月23日起復課　中一中五及中六等首先復課<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄宣布，全港中小學及幼稚園將在9月23日起、分兩階段恢復面授課程。楊潤雄表示，由於疫情緩和，具備恢復面授課程的條件，中一、中五、中六，及小一、小五、小六，以及幼稚園高班的學生，將可以在9月23日首階段恢復面授課堂。第二階段、即其他年級均可以在9月29日恢復面授課程。他表示，9月16日起學校可以讓少部分學生返學，進行不多於半日的面授課程，以全校1/6的學生為上限。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-31 15:04:29 (1)<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死"},{"pid":"4ea16c963c45d624a5ad5b583a394510d1b9aad8","tid":2182220,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"駁唔刀"},{"pid":"8e81169fe877599bc7dccdfe1dd4c9923adbfeec","tid":2182220,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea16c963c45d624a5ad5b583a394510d1b9aad8","tid":2182220,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"駁唔刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"Ching 點睇自己俾哥狗投閑置散"},{"pid":"739b93254c829b29ce7b471022dec52623ce8f11","tid":2182220,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e81169fe877599bc7dccdfe1dd4c9923adbfeec","tid":2182220,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea16c963c45d624a5ad5b583a394510d1b9aad8","tid":2182220,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"駁唔刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"Ching 點睇自己俾哥狗投閑置散"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"我打左閘勁撚過黑鳩Mendy啦屌你老母哥狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddc67d223bb943d09c136cdacf764e634e80d37","tid":2182220,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"739b93254c829b29ce7b471022dec52623ce8f11","tid":2